00:18:43.150 --> 00:18:45.531
Agora, nosso amigo,

00:18:45.532 --> 00:18:48.816
nosso filho, nosso confidente,

00:18:48.817 --> 00:18:50.489
nosso irmão,

00:18:50.490 --> 00:18:53.524
